\id 1JN Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular
\mt1 ∆ÅATAKURU YUUHANNA ARANURU NDUN
\c 1
\s1 Fii Daaluyee Ngurndan …óan
\p 
\v 1 Ko wonnoo kon gila ka fu…ó…óoode, ko …óun men nani, men yi'iri gite amen …óen, men punnii, men meemiri juu…óe amen …óen, …óun ko daaluyee ngurndan …óan.
\v 2 Awa, ngurndan …óan fee…≤ii, men yi'ii …óan, me…óen seeditanaade …óan. Me…óen fe…≤…≤inande on *ngurndan poomayankejan …óan, …óan wondunoo…óan e Baabaajo on, …óan fe…≤…≤inanaama men.
\v 3 Me…óen hollitude on onon kadi ko men yi'i kon e ko men nani kon fii no laatoron humondir…ìe e amen e nder humondiral men e Baabaajo on e ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu on.
\v 4 Me…óen windude …óun…óoo fii no weltaare men nden timmira.
\s1 Fii Wonugol ka Ndaygu
\p 
\v 5 E hino kibaaru mo men naniri mo on, me…óen …ìanginande on mo: Alla ko ndaygu, niwre woo alaa e makko.
\v 6 Si en innii hi…óen humondiri e makko, kono hi…óen yahude e nder niwre nden, haray en fenii, en wuuriraali goonga on.
\v 7 Kono si tawii hi…óen yahude e nder ndaygu ngun, wano o woniri non kanko tigi ka nder ndaygu, haray hi…óen humondiri, …óun haray ∆¥ii∆¥an Iisaa ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on no *la…ì…ìinde en e kala junuubu.
\p 
\v 8 Si en innii en aldaa e junuubu, haray en …óaynitike enen tigi, …óun haray goonga on alaa e men.
\v 9 Si en qirritike non junuubaaji men …óin, Alla ko Sella-Findeejo, Feewu…óo, o yaafanto en junuubaaji men …óin, o la…ì…ìina en e kala bonnere.
\v 10 Si en innii en wa…óaali junuubu, haray en wa…óii mo fenoowo, …óun haray daaluyee makko on alaa e men.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Fay…ìe an, mi…óo windande on …óun…óoo fii wota on wa…óu junuubu. Kono si go…ó…óo aru e wa…óude junuubu, haray hi…óen mari Fattantoo…óo en moggo Baabaajo on, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu, Feewu…óo on.
\v 2 Ko fii kanko tigi ko o sadaka fii no he…ìiren yaafuyee junuubaaji men …óin,\f a \fr 2:2 \ft 2.2 Wo…ì…ìe kadi no faamira: ¬´sadaka …óahoowo tikkere Alla nden.¬ª\f* hinaa non fii …ói men …óin tun, kono ko fii …ói …ìe aduna on fow.
\p 
\v 3 Si en …óoftike yamirooje makko …óen, haray hi…óen felliti wonde hi…óen andi mo.
\v 4 Kala on wi'u…óo no andi mo, hara o …óoftaaki yamirooje makko …óen, haray ko o fenoowo, goonga on alaa e makko.
\v 5 Kono kala …óoftii…óo daaluyee makko on, haray giggol Alla ngol no timmi e makko, ko non andirten hi…óen humondiri e makko.
\v 6 Kala on wi'u…óo no humondiri e makko, haray no haani wuurirde wano *Almasiihu on wuurirnoo non.
\p 
\v 7 Yi…ì…ìe, hinaa yamiroore heyre mi woni windande on, ko yamiroore hinnde, nde he…ìuno…óon gila ka fu…ó…óoode. Ndee yamiroore hinnde, ko ngol kongol ngol nanu…óon.
\v 8 Kono fow e mun, ko yamiroore heyre mi woni windande on. Haqiiqa mayre on no …ìangi e makko, no …ìangi e mon, ko fii niwre nden no fe∆¥∆¥ude, awa kadi ndaygu haqiiqawu ngun ndaygii toode.
\p 
\v 9 On wi'u…óo no ka ndaygu e hoore a…≤ugol musi…ó…óo mun, haray haa jooni himo ka niwre.
\v 10 On mo yi…ói musi…ó…óo mun, haray himo ka ndaygu, peggal woo alanaa mo.
\v 11 Kono on a…≤u…óo musi…ó…óo mun ko ka niwre woni, ko e nder niwre o woni yahude, o andaa ka o woni yaarude, ko fii niwre nden wuminii gite makko …óen.
\p 
\v 12 Mi…óo windande on, yo fay…ìe, …ìay junuubaaji mon …óin yaaforaama sabu innde makko nden.
\p 
\v 13 Mi…óo windande on, yo baabiraa…ìe, …ìay on andii on Woodanoo…óo gila ka fu…ó…óoode.
\p Mi…óo windande on, yo sukaa…ìe, …ìay on foolii bon…óo on.
\p 
\v 14 Mi windanii on kadi, yo fay…ìe, …ìay on andii Baabaajo on.
\p Mi windanii on kadi, yo baabiraa…ìe, …ìay on andii Woodanoo…óo on gila ka fu…ó…óoode.
\p Mi windanii on kadi, yo sukaa…ìe, …ìay hi…óon tii…ói, daaluyee Alla on no e mon, awa kadi on foolii bon…óo on.
\s1 Fii A…≤ugol oo Aduna ∆Åoylii…óo
\p 
\v 15 Wota on yi…óu aduna on e ko woni e aduna on kon. On mo yi…ói aduna on, haray giggol Baabaajo on alaa e makko.
\v 16 Ko fii kala ko woni e oo aduna, …óun ko mbelee…óe …ìandu e himmangol ko yi'i e mantorgol keyeeji aduna, hinaa e Baabaajo on iwri, kono ko e oo aduna.
\v 17 Awa oo aduna e himmeeji mun ko ko woni fe∆¥∆¥ude, kono on wa…óoowo faale Alla on luttay haa poomaa.
\s1 Fii Reenagol e Dartotoo…ìe Almasiihu on …ìen
\p 
\v 18 Awa, yo fay…ìe, ko saa'i sakkitoro on nii. Wano nanir…óon non, liddotoo…óo Almasiihu on aray, e hay fewndo …óoo toode liddotoo…ìe Almasiihu on …óuu…óu…ìe arii. Ko nii andirten wonde ko saa'i sakkitoro on nii.
\v 19 ∆Åen non ko e men iwi, kono hinaa …ìe men, ko fii si …ìe wonno …ìe men, …ìe luttidayno e men. Kono …óun …ìanginii wonde …ìe fow wonaa …ìe men.
\p 
\v 20 Onon kan, *Senii…óo on ye…óii on Ruuhu mun on, ko …óun wa…ói si on fow hi…óon mari andal.
\v 21 Mi windiranaali on wa si tawii on andaa goonga on, kono ko …ìay hi…óon andi, e hi…óon andi kadi wonde fenaande woo iwataa e goonga.
\v 22 Ko hombo non woni on fenoowo, si hinaa on yeddu…óo wonde Iisaa ko Almasiihu? On ko liddotoo…óo Almasiihu on, yeddu…óo Baabaajo on e ∆Åi…ó…óo on.
\v 23 Awa kala yeddu…óo ∆Åi…ó…óo on he…ìaali Baabaajo on, kala qirritii…óo ∆Åi…ó…óo on, haray he…ìii Baabaajo on.
\p 
\v 24 Onon non, ko nanu…óon kon gila ka fu…ó…óoode no haani wonude ka …ìer…óe mon. Si tawii ko nanu…óon kon gila ka fu…ó…óoode wonii ka …ìer…óe mon, haray onon kadi on humondirii e ∆Åi…ó…óo on e Baabaajo on.
\v 25 Awa e hino fodaari ndi o wa…óani en ndin: ko *ngurndan poomayankejan …óan.
\p 
\v 26 Mi windiranii on …óun e telen-ma won…ìe …óaynude on …ìen.
\v 27 Ko fii onon, Ruuhu mo he…ìir…óon Almasiihu on no e mon, ko …óun wa…ói on hatonjinaa e janneede, kono, wano Ruuhu makko on woni jannirde on piiji …óin fow non, (ko mo goonga, mo aldaa e fenaande), humondiree e Almasiihu on wano Ruuhu makko on janniri on non.
\s1 Fii Fay…ìe Alla …ìen
\p 
\v 28 Jooni non, yo fay…ìe, humondiree e makko, fii, nde o fee…≤oyi, yo en he…ìu hoolaare, e nde o ari, wota en hersu yeeso makko.
\v 29 Si tawii hi…óon andi ko o Feewu…óo, haray andee kala wa…óu…óo ko feewi ko jibinannde makko.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Ndaaree noone giggol ngol Baabaajo on ye…ói en ngol, haa nodda…óen fay…ìe Alla. Awa kadi ko en …óun. E hino ko wa…ói kon si aduna on andaa en, ko fii o andaali mo.
\v 2 Yi…ì…ìe, jooni non ko en fay…ìe Alla. Ko wonoyten kon fe…≤…≤inaaka taho. Kono hi…óen andi, nde o fee…≤oyi, en nandoyay e makko, ko fii en yi'oyay mo wano o woniri non.
\v 3 Kala jogii…óo on tama'u e makko, haray no la…ì…ìintinii wano kanko *Almasiihu on o laa…ìiri non.
\p 
\v 4 Kala non on wa…óu…óo junuubu, haray ontigi bonnii Sariya on, ko fii junuubu ko bonnugol Sariya.
\v 5 Kono hi…óon andi, kanko Almasiihu on ko o fee…≤iri ko fii ittugol junuubaaji, e hin-le junuubu alaa e makko.
\v 6 Kala on humondir…óo e makko duumotaako e wa…óugol junuubu. Kala non wa…óoowo junuubu, haray yi'aali mo, andaali mo.
\p 
\v 7 Ko onon, yo fay…ìe, wota hay gooto …óaynu on, ko fii kala on wa…óu…óo ko feewi, haray ko feewu…óo, wano kanko Almasiihu on o woniri feewu…óo non.
\v 8 Kala non on wa…óoowo junuubu, haray ko mo Ibuliisa, ko fii gila ka fu…ó…óoode Ibuliisa no wa…óude junuubu. *∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on-le ko fee…≤iri ko fii mulugol kuu…óe Ibuliisa …óen.
\v 9 Kala on jibinaa…óo immorde e Alla duumotaako e wa…óugol junuubu, ko fii haray awdi Alla ndin no e makko, haray o waawataa wa…óude junuubu, …ìay ko e immorde e Alla woni ko o jibinaa.
\v 10 Awa e hino ko …ìangini hakkunde fay…ìe Alla …ìen e fay…ìe Ibuliisa …ìen: kala on mo wa…óataa ko feewi, haray hinaa mo Alla, ko wano non kadi on mo yi…óaa musi…ó…óo mun.
\s1 Fii Yi…óindirgol
\p 
\v 11 E hino kibaaru mo nanu…óon on gila ka fu…ó…óoode: yi…óindiren.
\v 12 Wota en wa'u wa Qaayiina\f b \fr 3:12 \ft 3.12 \it ¬´Qaayiina¬ª\it* no wi'ee kadi \it ¬´Qaabiila¬ª.\it* Fu…ó. 4 \f*, on mo Ibuliisa, warunoo…óo mi…≤…≤iraawo mun on. E ko fii hon…óun o warannoo mo? Ko tawde kuu…óe makko …óen kanko Qaayiina ko bon…óe, …óe mi…≤…≤iraawo makko on …óen kan ko feewu…óe.
\v 13 Musi…ì…ìe an, si tawii aduna on no a…≤i on, haray wota on ≈ãal…óu.
\v 14 Ko fii hi…óen andi ko e mayde iwu…óen, aru…óen e ngurndan, …ìay hi…óen yi…ói musi…ì…ìe men …ìen. On mo alaa giggol, haray ko ka mayde woni.
\v 15 Kala on a…≤u…óo musi…ó…óo mun, haray ko waroowo. Hi…óon andi-le kala waroowo, haray *ngurndan poomayankejan alaa e makko.
\p 
\v 16 E hino no andirten ko woni giggol: Almasiihu on okkitirii ngurndan mun …óan fii men, haray enen kadi hi…óen haani okkitirde ngurndan men …óan fii musi…ì…ìe men …ìen.
\v 17 Si tawii go…ó…óo no mari ngaluuji aduna, o yi'ii musi…ó…óo makko sokol…óo, o ombanii mo gite, haray ko honno giggol Alla ngol wonirta e makko?
\v 18 Ko onon, yo fay…ìe, wota en yi…óir kongol maa …óenngal tun, kono yi…óiren kuugal e goonga.
\v 19 Ko nii andirten ko en …ìe goonga, …ìer…óe men …óen he…ìirta kadi hoolaare yeeso makko.
\v 20 Hay si …ìer…óe men …óen no felude en, Alla no …ìuri …ìer…óe men …óen mawnude, e himo andi fow.
\p 
\v 21 Awa, yo yi…ì…ìe, si tawii …ìer…óe men …óen felaali en, haray hi…óen mari hoolaare yeeso Alla.
\v 22 Kala ko tori…óen mo, en he…ìiray mo, …ìay hi…óen …óoftii yamirooje makko …óen, hi…óen wa…óude ko welata mo.
\v 23 Awa e hino yamiroore makko nden: ko yo en gom…óin innde ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu on, yi…óindiren kadi wano o yamiri en non.
\v 24 Kala on …óoftii…óo yamirooje makko …óen, haray no humondiri e Alla, Alla kadi no humondiri e makko. Awa kadi e hino no andirten wonde himo humondiri e men: ko *Ruuhu Senii…óo mo o ye…ói en on andir…óen …óun.
\c 4
\s1 Fii Ndarndagol Ruuhuuji …óin
\p 
\v 1 Ko onon, yo yi…ì…ìe, wota on hoolo kala ne…ó…óo wi'u…óo Ruuhu Alla on no e makko, kono taskee …ìe fii andugol si ruuhu won…óo e ma…ì…ìe on ko e Alla iwri, ko fii wa…óitii…ìe annaba …óuu…óu…ìe arii e oo aduna.
\v 2 E hino no andirton si kongu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin ko e Ruuhu Alla on iwri: kala qirritii…óo wonde Iisaa Almasiihu on wontuno ne…ó…óo, o ari ka aduna, haray ko mo Alla.
\v 3 Kala non mo qirritaaki Iisaa, haray hinaa mo Ruuhu Alla on, haray on ko mo liddotoo…óo *Almasiihu on, on mo nanuno…óon no arude. On non jooni no e aduna on.
\p 
\v 4 Ko onon, yo fay…ìe, ko on …ìe Alla, awa kadi on foolii wa…óitii…ìe annaba …ìen, ko fii Won…óo e mon on no …ìuri mawnude won…óo e aduna on.
\v 5 ∆Åen ko …ìe oo aduna, ko …óun wa…ói kongu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin ko …ói oo aduna, awa kadi aduna on no he…óaade …ói.
\v 6 Enen-le, ko en …ìe Alla. Kala on andu…óo Alla he…óoto en, kono on mo tawata non wonaa mo Alla he…óotaako en. Ko non andirten Ruuhu Goongaajo on e ruuhu fenaandeejo on.
\s1 Fii Giggol Alla ngol e Yi…óindirgol men ngol
\p 
\v 7 Ko onon, yo yi…ì…ìe, yi…óindiren, ko fii giggol ko ka Alla iwri, awa kala yi…óu…óo ko jibinaa…óo immorde e Alla, haray himo andi Alla.
\v 8 Kala mo aldaa e giggol, haray andaa Alla, ko fii Alla ko giggol.
\v 9 E hino no giggol Alla ngol fee…≤iri e men: Allaahu on addii ∆Åi…ó…óo makko bajjo on e nder oo aduna fii no wuuriren immorde e makko.
\v 10 E hino ko woni ngol giggol kon: hinaa ko yi…óu…óen Alla kon, kono ko ko o yi…ói en kon, o addiri ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on sadaka fii no he…ìiren yaafuyee junuubaaji men …óin.
\v 11 ∆Åay Alla yi…óirii en nii, yo yi…ì…ìe, haray enen kadi hi…óen haani yi…óindirde.
\v 12 Hay gooto yi'aali Alla haa hande, kono si en yi…óindirii, haray Alla no humondiri e men, giggol makko wonungol e men ngol timma.
\p 
\v 13 E hino no andirten hi…óen humondiri e makko, kanko kadi himo humondiri e men: ko sabu Ruuhu makko mo o ye…ói en on.
\v 14 Menen non men yi'ii, me…óen seeditaade wonde Baabaajo on nulii ∆Åi…ó…óo on fii dandugol aduna on.
\v 15 Kala on qirritii…óo wonde Iisaa ko *∆Åi…ó…óo Alla, haray Alla no humondiri e makko, kanko kadi himo humondiri e Alla.
\v 16 Awa, enen en andii, en gom…óinii giggol ngol Alla yi…ói en ngol.
\p Alla ko giggol. Kala on wondu…óo e giggol, haray himo humondiri e Alla, Alla kadi no humondiri e makko.
\v 17 Ko nii giggol ngol timmiri e men, fii no he…ìiren hoolaare …≤ande …≤aawoore nden. Wano o woniri non kanko, enen kadi ko non wonir…óen e oo aduna.
\v 18 Kulol alaa e nder giggol, kono giggol timmungol ra…óoto kulol, …ìay kulol no tijjii donkineede. Awa kadi, kala on hulu…óo, haray giggol ngol timmaa e makko.
\v 19 Enen non hi…óen yi…ói, …ìay ko kanko adii en yi…óude.
\v 20 On mo wi'i no yi…ói Alla, e hoore himo a…≤i musi…ó…óo makko, haray ko fenoowo. Ko fii on mo yi…óaali musi…ó…óo mun mo o renti on, haray o waawataa yi…óude Alla mo o rentaa on.
\v 21 Awa, ko ndee yamiroore …óoo he…ìir…óen mo: mo no yi…ói Alla, yo yi…óu kadi musi…ó…óo mun on.
\c 5
\s1 Fii Gom…óingol ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on
\p 
\v 1 Kala on gom…óin…óo wonde ko Iisaa woni *Almasiihu on, haray ko jibinaa…óo immorde e Alla, e kala yi…óu…óo Baabaajo on yi…óay ∆Åi…ó…óo on kadi.
\v 2 E hino no andirten hi…óen yi…ói fay…ìe Alla …ìen: ko si en yi…óii Alla, en …óoftike yamirooje makko …óen.
\v 3 Ko woni yi…óugol Alla: ko …óoftagol yamirooje makko …óen. Yamirooje makko …óen-le hinaa sattu…óe,
\v 4 ko fii on jibinaa…óo ka Alla foolay oo aduna. Awa e hino polgal foolungal aduna on: ko gom…óinal men ngal.
\v 5 Ko hombo woni on foolu…óo aduna on, si hinaa on gom…óin…óo wonde Iisaa ko *∆Åi…ó…óo Alla?
\p 
\v 6 Ko kanko Iisaa Almasiihu on ardi e ndiyan e ∆¥ii∆¥an, hinaa non ndiyan tun o ardi, kono ko ndiyan e ∆¥ii∆¥an. Awa ko Ruuhu Allaahu on woni seeditaade, …ìay on Ruuhu ko o goonga.
\v 7 Ko fii ko piiji tati woni seeditaade:
\v 8 ko Ruuhu Allaahu on e ndiyan …óan e ∆¥ii∆¥an …óan, …óin non tati hi…ói fotti.
\v 9 Hi…óen ja…ìude seeditooje yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko seeditoore Alla nden …ìuri mawnude, …óun ko seeditoore nde Alla seeditii fii ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on nden.
\v 10 Kala on gom…óin…óo ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on, haray nden seeditoore no e makko. Kono on mo gom…óinaa Alla non, haray o wa…óii mo fenoowo, ko fii haray o gom…óinaa seeditoore nde Alla seeditii fii ∆Åi…ó…óo mun on nden.
\v 11 Awa e hino nden seeditoore: Alla okkii en *ngurndan poomayankejan, …óan ngurndan non no e ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on.
\v 12 Kala humondir…óo e ∆Åi…ó…óo on no mari ngurndan …óan. Kala mo humondiraa e ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on haray alaa …óan ngurndan.
\s1 Fii Kongu…ói Rawnor…ói …óin
\p 
\v 13 Mi windanii on …óun fii no andiron wonde hi…óon mari ngurndan poomayankejan, onon …ìee gom…óin…ìe e innde ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on.
\v 14 Awa e hino hoolaare nde …ìattorten Alla nden: si en torike mo go…ó…óun ko yaadi e faale makko on, o he…óoto en.
\v 15 ∆Åay non hi…óen andi himo he…óii kala ko tori…óen mo, haray hi…óen andi en he…ìii ko tori…óen mo kon.
\v 16 On mo yi'i musi…ó…óo mun no wa…óa junuubu mo nawrataa e mayde, yo o torano mo, Alla ye…óay mo ngurndan, …óun non ko …ìen wa…óoo…ìe junuubu mo nawrataa e mayde. Kono no woodi junuubu nawroowo e mayde, hinaa fii on junuubu mi wi'i yo tore.
\v 17 Kala ko aldaa e peewal ko junuubu, kono no woodi non junuubaaji …ói nawrataa e mayde.
\p 
\v 18 Hi…óen andi kala on jibinaa…óo immorde e Alla, o duumotaako e wa…óugol junuubu, kono ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on reenay mo, danda mo, hara Bon…óo on meemataa mo.
\v 19 Hi…óen andi ko en …ìe Alla, awa kadi aduna on fow no e ley doole Bon…óo on.
\v 20 Hi…óen andi kadi ∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on arii, o okkii en faamu fii andugol Goongaajo on. Hi…óen humondiri-le e Goongaajo on, …ìay hi…óen humondiri e ∆Åi…ó…óo makko on, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu. Ko on woni Alla Goongaajo on e ngurndan poomayankejan …óan.
\p 
\v 21 Ko onon, yo fay…ìe, reenee e sanamuuji …óin!
